{
  "stem": "3855.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[POINTS] We were issued toothpaste and a toothbrush.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I want you to understand getting to that German mentality.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Our head was shaven, which was difficult in my case because was-- hair was sticking to my blood.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But he did a reasonable job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the next time he took it all off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we were warned that there is an unpredictable inspection of toothbrushes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "If the toothbrush is dirty, you will be punished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Now we saw what punishment meant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Believe me, it was amazing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I was assigned to, to be a food carrier.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Every time the bell rang, some of us would run to the kitchen, which I want to tell you was stainless steel from A to Z.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was organized to the nth degree.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we would get this soup or this chicory coffee in this huge tub.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And two would run down this long runway to-- our building was almost in the back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And then we would ladle it out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We weren't permitted to eat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We would ladle it out to the guys standing at this huge table with a little tin dish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Sunday we had soup.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But on the way back, we were permitted to eat whatever was left in these huge drums.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We had our tin cup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "It was the chicory coffee with a piece of dark bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Or it was the soup on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It was the probably muggy-chicken flavored.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] There was no chicken in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But it smelt like and tasted like chicken.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "We were permitted to take as much as we could on the way back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And that's how the food carriers didn't lose weight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the rest of the day, we marched continuously.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "We marched from morning till night.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
